age.Name: age
age.SQL: select datediff(year, birth_date, getDate()) as AGE from super_daily.dbo.patient p inner join super_daily.dbo.identity_id i on i.pat_id = p.pat_id where identity_type_id = 3 and identity_id = iid

ancillary_testing.Name: ancillary_testing
ancillary_testing.SQL: select ancillary_testing, DATE_OF_SURGERY from super_adhoc.dbo.gic_colorectal_info gci inner join super_adhoc.dbo.gic_patient_dem_info gpdi on gpdi.dem_id = gci.dem_id where NYP_MRN = id and DATE_OF_SURGERY between timestamp_min and timestamp_max

bio_g_number.Name: bio_g_number
bio_g_number.SQL: select cast(t3.value as varchar) as g_number,cast(t4.value as varchar) as collection_date from [super_staging].[dbo].[REDCAP_DATA] as t3 inner join super_staging.dbo.REDCAP_DATA as t4 on t3.project_id=t4.project_id and t3.event_id=t4.event_id and t3.record=t4.record where t3.project_id='1971' and t3.event_id='7607' and t3.field_name='g_number' and t4.field_name='collection_date' and t3.record in( SELECT distinct t1.[record] FROM [super_staging].[dbo].[REDCAP_DATA] t1 where t1.project_id='1971' and t1.event_id='7607' and t1.field_name='pat_mrn' and cast(t1.value as nvarchar) like %id%)

bio_gi_number.Name: bio_gi_number
bio_gi_number.SQL: select cast(t3.value as varchar) as gi_number,cast(t4.value as varchar) as biospecimen_id from [super_staging].[dbo].[REDCAP_DATA] as t3 inner join super_staging.dbo.REDCAP_DATA as t4 on t3.project_id=t4.project_id and t3.event_id=t4.event_id and t3.record=t4.record where t3.project_id='1971' and t3.event_id='7607' and t3.field_name='g_number' and t4.field_name='biospecimen_id' and t3.record in( SELECT distinct t1.[record] FROM [super_staging].[dbo].[REDCAP_DATA] t1 where t1.project_id='1971' and t1.event_id='7607' and t1.field_name='pat_mrn' and cast(t1.value as varchar) like %id%)

dx_name.Name: dx_name
dx_name.SQL: select DX_NAME, dx.CONTACT_DATE from super_monthly.dbo.clarity_edg edg inner join super_monthly.dbo.pat_enc_dx dx on dx.dx_id = edg.dx_id inner join super_daily.dbo.identity_id i on i.pat_id = dx.pat_id where identity_type_id = 3 and identity_id = iid and contact_date between timestamp_min and timestamp_max order by contact_date desc

dx_name_agg1.Name: dx_name_agg1
dx_name_agg1.SQL: ;with agg as (select top 20 DX_NAME, dx.CONTACT_DATE, row_number() over (order by contact_date desc) as diagrank from super_monthly.dbo.clarity_edg edg inner join super_monthly.dbo.pat_enc_dx dx on dx.dx_id = edg.dx_id inner join super_daily.dbo.identity_id i on i.pat_id = dx.pat_id where identity_type_id = 3 and identity_id = iid and contact_date between timestamp_min and timestamp_max) select * from agg where diagrank = 1

immuno_his_ass_msi.Name: immuno_his_ass_msi
immuno_his_ass_msi.SQL: select coalesce(pre_mlh1_msh2_6_pms2,loss_mlh1,loss_msh2,loss_msh6,loss_pms2) as immuno_type, DATE_OF_SURGERY from super_adhoc.dbo.gic_colorectal_info gci inner join super_adhoc.dbo.gic_patient_dem_info gpdi on gpdi.dem_id = gci.dem_id where NYP_MRN = id and DATE_OF_SURGERY between timestamp_min and timestamp_max

insurance_name.Name: insurance_name
insurance_name.SQL: select PAYOR_NAME, CONTACT_DATE from super_daily.dbo.patient p inner join super_monthly.dbo.clarity_epm epm on epm.payor_id = p.prim_epm_id inner join super_monthly.dbo.pat_enc pe on p.pat_id = pe.pat_id inner join super_daily.dbo.identity_id i on p.pat_id = i.pat_id where payor_name is not null and identity_type_id = 3 and identity_id = iid and contact_date between timestamp_min and timestamp_max;

insurance_type.Name: insurance_type
insurance_type.SQL: select BENEFIT_PLAN_NAME, CONTACT_DATE from super_daily.dbo.patient p inner join super_monthly.dbo.clarity_epp epp on epp.benefit_plan_id = p.prim_epp_id inner join super_monthly.dbo.pat_enc pe on p.pat_id = pe.pat_id inner join super_daily.dbo.identity_id i on p.pat_id = i.pat_id where benefit_plan_name is not null and identity_type_id = 3 and identity_id = iid and contact_date between timestamp_min and timestamp_max;

kras_mut_wt.Name: kras_mut_wt

dx_enc_bulk.Name: dx_enc_bulk
dx_enc_bulk.SQL: select distinct top 50 edg.current_icd10_list as CURRENT_ICD10_DIAGNOSIS, dx.CONTACT_DATE as CONTACT_DATE_P from super_monthly.dbo.clarity_edg edg inner join super_monthly.dbo.pat_enc_dx dx on dx.dx_id = edg.dx_id inner join super_daily.dbo.identity_id i on i.pat_id = dx.pat_id where identity_type_id = 3 and identity_id = iid and contact_date between timestamp_min and timestamp_max ORDER BY CONTACT_DATE_P desc

smrtdta_nadir_cd34_count.Name: smrtdta_nadir_cd34_count
smrtdta_nadir_cd34_count.SQL: SELECT SV.SMRTDTA_ELEM_VALUE AS MEAS_VALUE, SD.CUR_VALUE_DATETIME as RECORDED_TIME FROM super_monthly.dbo.SMRTDTA_ELEM_DATA SD INNER JOIN super_monthly.dbo.SMRTDTA_ELEM_VALUE SV ON SD.HLV_ID = SV.HLV_ID inner join super_daily.dbo.IDENTITY_ID i ON i.PAT_ID = SD.RECORD_ID_VARCHAR WHERE SD.ELEMENT_ID  = 'WMCHIST#601401' and identity_type_id = 3 and SV.SMRTDTA_ELEM_VALUE is not null and identity_id = iid and SD.CUR_VALUE_DATETIME between timestamp_min and timestamp_max

smrtdta_hiv_date_diagnosis.Name: smrtdta_hiv_date_diagnosis
smrtdta_hiv_date_diagnosis.SQL: SELECT min(cast(DD.CALENDAR_DT as date)) AS MEAS_VALUE FROM super_monthly.dbo.SMRTDTA_ELEM_DATA SD INNER JOIN super_monthly.dbo.SMRTDTA_ELEM_VALUE SV ON SD.HLV_ID = SV.HLV_ID inner join super_daily.dbo.IDENTITY_ID i on i.PAT_ID=sd.RECORD_ID_VARCHAR LEFT OUTER JOIN super_monthly.dbo.DATE_DIMENSION DD ON SV.SMRTDTA_ELEM_VALUE = DD.EPIC_DTE WHERE SD.ELEMENT_ID  = 'WMCHIST#601400' and identity_type_id = 3 and DD.CALENDAR_DT is not null and identity_id = iid

orders_hiv_viral_load_recent_date.Name: orders_hiv_viral_load_recent_date
orders_hiv_viral_load_recent_date.SQL: SELECT max(ORR.RESULT_DATE) AS LAST_DATE FROM super_monthly.dbo.ORDER_PROC OP INNER JOIN super_monthly.dbo.ORDER_RESULTS ORR ON OP.ORDER_PROC_ID = ORR.ORDER_PROC_ID inner join super_daily.dbo.IDENTITY_ID i on i.pat_id=op.PAT_ID WHERE ORR.COMPONENT_ID IN (149,550,676,677,4179,4181,5701514,5701506) AND ORR.ORD_NUM_VALUE <> 9999999 and identity_type_id = 3 and identity_id = iid

orders_cd4_recent_date.Name: orders_cd4_recent_date
orders_cd4_recent_date.SQL: SELECT max(ORR.RESULT_DATE) AS LAST_DATE FROM super_monthly.dbo.ORDER_PROC OP INNER JOIN super_monthly.dbo.ORDER_RESULTS ORR ON OP.ORDER_PROC_ID = ORR.ORDER_PROC_ID INNER JOIN super_monthly.dbo.CLARITY_COMPONENT CC ON ORR.COMPONENT_ID = CC.COMPONENT_ID inner join super_daily.dbo.identity_id i on i.pat_id=op.PAT_ID WHERE CC.BASE_NAME = 'CD4COUNT' AND ORR.ORD_NUM_VALUE <> 9999999 and identity_type_id = 3 and identity_id = iid

marital_status.Name: marital_status
marital_status.SQL: select name from super_monthly.dbo.zc_marital_status ms inner join super_daily.dbo.patient p on p.MARITAL_STATUS_C = ms.MARITAL_STATUS_C inner join super_daily.dbo.identity_id i on i.pat_id = p.pat_id where identity_type_id = 3 and identity_id = iid

language_spoken.Name: language_spoken
language_spoken.SQL: select name from super_monthly.dbo.zc_LANGUAGE la inner join super_daily.dbo.patient p on p.LANGUAGE_C = la.LANGUAGE_C inner join super_daily.dbo.identity_id i on i.pat_id = p.pat_id where identity_type_id = 3 and identity_id = iid

PUL_ICU_PRE_EVAL_VASOPRESSORS_STARTED.Name: VASOPRESSORS_STARTED
PUL_ICU_PRE_EVAL_VASOPRESSORS_STARTED.SQL: SELECT VASOPRESSORS_STARTED = case when DOPAMINE ='Y' then 'Y' when dobutamine ='Y' then 'Y' when norepinephrine ='Y' then 'Y' when ephinephrine ='Y' then 'Y' when Milrinone ='Y' then 'Y' when vasopressin ='Y' then 'Y' else 'N' END, cast(IPE.start_date as date) ICU_DATE FROM [DM_PLMNRY].[CEDAR].[EVALUATION_PRE_REDCAP] IPE join [DM_PLMNRY].[CEDAR].[ICU_VISITS_REDCAP] cie on cie.clientguid = IPE.ClientGUID join SUPER_DAILY.dbo.IDENTITY_ID i on cie.mrn=i.IDENTITY_ID where IDENTITY_TYPE_ID='3' and IDENTITY_ID = iid and cast(IPE.start_date as date) between timestamp_min and timestamp_max
